```

### Avoid This Format
```markdown
1. [`ACTIVITY_ollama_local.md`](ACTIVITY_ollama_local.md)
2. [Run Ollama Locally](ACTIVITY_ollama_local.md) (missing prefix)
```

### Good File Reference (for code/script files)
```markdown
See the [`plumber.R`](plumber.R) file for the API implementation.
```

### Good Section with Icon
