- [ ] Includes banner and footer images with relative links
- [ ] Has a complete Table of Contents with anchor links showing order of activities
- [ ] **Concise and focused**: Acts as a navigation guide, not detailed instructions
- [ ] **Activities section**: Numbered list (1., 2., 3., etc.) showing sequence
  - [ ] Uses human-readable names (titles) as link text with appropriate prefixes (ACTIVITY:, READ:, LAB:) for ACTIVITY_, READ_, and LAB_ files
  - [ ] Includes ACTIVITY_, READ_, and LAB_ files that are part of the workflow
  - [ ] Sub-items (indented with `-`) list related files like example scripts
  - [ ] Each item has a brief description after the link (if needed)
