- [ ] Uses icons frequently and appropriately
- [ ] Uses bold, italics, and formatting effectively
- [ ] Tone is concise and humble (no "obvious" or "critical" phrases)
- [ ] Content is appropriate for graduate students new to Git/AI/APIs
- [ ] Avoids extensive descriptions; refers to individual files for details
- [ ] Includes "Back to Top" link in footer
